改めて今日は博衣こより生誕ライブ2026にお越しいただきありがとうございます！
Once again, thank you for joining Hakuikoyori Birthday Live 2026 today!

172
00:09:44,508 --> 00:09:50,008
コメントもいっぱいありがとう！イエーイ！こっ、こよ、見えてるよ、ありがとう！
Thanks for all the comments! Yay! I see you, Kok-koyo, thank you!

173
00:09:50,508 --> 00:10:00,008
ということで、ライブの感想やスクショはハッシュタグ #博衣こよ生誕Live2026 をつけてたくさん...
So, please share your thoughts and screenshots with the hashtag #HakuikoyoriBirthdayLive2026!

174
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:01,316
ポストしてください！
Please post about it!

175
00:10:01,316 --> 00:10:06,016
目指せトレンド1位、よろしくだああ！
Let's aim for trending #1! Here we go!

176
00:10:06,316 --> 00:10:10,016
はい、ということで。ちょっと、息が整ってないですけど...
Alright! I'm a bit out of breath, but...

177
00:10:10,016 --> 00:10:13,316
さて、今年の生誕ライブ、テーマは...
Well, the theme for this year's birthday live is...

178
00:10:13,316 --> 00:10:16,516
「ゲームソングライブ」です！
"Game Song Live"!

179
00:10:16,816 --> 00:10:22,416
これまでたくさんやってきた実況配信で、一緒に遊んできた思い出のゲームや...
From the many game streams we've done together, full of memories...

180
00:10:22,416 --> 00:10:27,216
こよが大好きをゲーム関連の楽曲をたくさん詰め込みました。
...I've packed in lots of game-related songs that I love.

181
00:10:27,216 --> 00:10:30,416
最後まで全力で楽しんでってね！
Enjoy it with all your might until the very end!

182
00:10:30,516 --> 00:10:34,016
ということで、1曲目は大好きなポケモンの...
So, for the first song, I sang my favorite Pokemon's...

183
00:10:34,016 --> 00:10:36,416
「XYZ」を歌わせていただきました！ねー！
"XYZ"! Right?!

184
00:10:36,516 --> 00:10:40,516
助手くん、わー！
Joshu-kun, wah!

185
00:10:41,016 --> 00:10:44,816
「俺はこいつと旅に出る」っていうことです。
It means "I'm going on a journey with this guy."

186
00:10:46,016 --> 00:10:51,316
はい、Xでセトリ予想もね、みんなにたくさんしてもらってたんですけど...
I saw all your setlist predictions on X, but...

187
00:10:51,316 --> 00:10:56,516
ポケモンの予想は結構多かったけど、XYZ当てられてる人は結構少なかったです。
There were many Pokemon guesses, but very few people got "XYZ" right.

188
00:10:56,516 --> 00:10:59,516
当たった君、おめでとう！
To those who got it, congratulations!

189
00:11:00,016 --> 00:11:04,316
まぁこの曲は、Z-Aが発表になったっていうのもあるんですけど...
Well, this song... partly because Pokemon Z-A was announced...

190
00:11:04,316 --> 00:11:08,516
歌詞がめっちゃ良くて、実はこよりにもぴったりな曲なので選びました。
But the lyrics are so good, and it's actually perfect for Koyori, so I chose it.

191
00:11:08,516 --> 00:11:14,516
さぁ、この後も、自分の予想が当たってるかなーって、ドキドキしながら楽しんでいってください。
Now, please keep enjoying and see if your predictions come true!

192
00:11:15,016 --> 00:11:18,016
新3Dお披露目もあるからね！
There's also a new 3D reveal!

193
00:11:18,016 --> 00:11:20,516
絶対に最後まで見てってね！
Make sure to watch until the very end!

194
00:11:21,016 --> 00:11:23,016
それでは、そろそろ次の曲。
Now, time for the next song.

195
00:11:24,016 --> 00:11:28,016
ゲームの世界へ、どうぞ！
Off to the game world we go!

196
00:12:14,516 --> 00:12:18,016
エアーマンが倒せない
I Can't Defeat Airman

197
00:12:24,516 --> 00:12:27,516
気がついたら　同じ面ばかりプレイ
Before I knew it, I was playing the same stage again and again

198
00:12:27,516 --> 00:12:30,016
そしていつも　同じ場所で死ぬ
And I always die in the same spot

199
00:12:33,516 --> 00:12:35,516
あきらめずに
Without giving up,

200
00:12:35,516 --> 00:12:38,516
消える足場に挑戦するけど
I'll keep jumping on the vanishing platforms,

201
00:12:38,516 --> 00:12:42,516
すぐに下に落ちるよ
But I immediately fall down

202
00:12:44,216 --> 00:12:48,816
アイテム2号があれば 楽に 向こうの 岸まで 着くけれど
If only I had Item 2, I could easily reach the other side...

203
00:12:49,016 --> 00:12:51,516
何回やっても 何回やっても
No matter how many times I try,

204
00:12:51,516 --> 00:12:54,016
エアーマンが倒せないよ
I can't defeat Airman!

205
00:12:54,016 --> 00:12:58,516
あの竜巻 何回やっても 避けれない
I can't dodge those tornadoes, no matter how many times I try

206
00:12:59,016 --> 00:13:01,516
後ろに回って 打ち続けても
Even if I get behind him and keep firing,

207
00:13:01,516 --> 00:13:03,516
いずれは風に飛ばされる
I'll eventually be blown away by the wind

208
00:13:04,016 --> 00:13:06,516
タイム連打も 試してみたけど
I even tried rapid-pausing,

209
00:13:06,516 --> 00:13:08,516
竜巻相手じゃ 意味がない
but it's useless against the tornado

210
00:13:09,016 --> 00:13:11,516
だから次は絶対 勝つために
So, to ensure a win next time,

211
00:13:11,516 --> 00:13:14,516
僕はE缶だけは 最後までとっておく
I'll save my E-Tanks until the very end!

212
00:13:39,016 --> 00:13:42,016
気がついたら ライフも 少ししかない
Before I knew it, I had very little life left

213
00:13:42,016 --> 00:13:46,016
そしていつも そこでE缶使う
And I always end up using an E-Tank there

214
00:13:48,516 --> 00:13:53,016
あきらめずに エアーマンまで たどり着くけれど
I don't give up and manage to reach Airman...

215
00:13:53,516 --> 00:13:57,516
すぐに 残機 なくなる
...but I immediately run out of lives

216
00:13:58,516 --> 00:14:03,016
リーフシールドがあれば 楽に エアーマンを 倒せるけど
If only I had the Leaf Shield, I could easily defeat Airman, but...

217
00:14:03,516 --> 00:14:06,016
何回やっても 何回やっても
No matter how many times I try,

218
00:14:06,016 --> 00:14:08,516
ウッドマンが倒せないよ
I can't defeat Woodman!

219
00:14:09,016 --> 00:14:13,016
落ちるこの葉 何回やっても 避けれない
I can't dodge those falling leaves, no matter how many times I try

220
00:14:13,516 --> 00:14:15,516
後ろに下がって 距離をとっても
Even if I back away and keep my distance,

221
00:14:15,516 --> 00:14:18,016
いずれは距離を詰められる
he eventually closes in

222
00:14:18,516 --> 00:14:21,016
タイム連打も 試してみたけど
I even tried rapid-pausing,

223
00:14:21,016 --> 00:14:23,016
あいつのジャンプは くぐれない
but I can't slide under his jumps

224
00:14:23,516 --> 00:14:26,016
だから次は絶対 勝つために
So, to ensure a win next time,

225
00:14:26,016 --> 00:14:29,016
僕はE缶だけは 最後までとっておく
I'll save my E-Tanks until the very end!

226
00:14:48,016 --> 00:14:52,516
アイテム2号があれば 楽に 向こうの 岸まで 着くけれど
If only I had Item 2, I could easily reach the other side...

227
00:14:53,016 --> 00:14:55,516
何回やっても 何回やっても
No matter how many times I try,

228
00:14:55,516 --> 00:14:58,516
エアーマンが倒せないよ
I can't defeat Airman!

229
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:01,224
何回やっても 何回やっても
No matter how many times I try, no matter how many times I try,

230
00:15:01,224 --> 00:15:02,824
エアーマンが倒せないよ
I can't defeat Airman!

231
00:15:02,824 --> 00:15:05,524
後ろに回って打ち続けても
Even if I get behind him and keep shooting,

232
00:15:05,524 --> 00:15:07,724
いずれは風に飛ばされる
I'll eventually be blown away by the wind.

233
00:15:07,724 --> 00:15:09,124
タイム連打も試してみたけど
I even tried spamming the Time Stopper,

234
00:15:09,124 --> 00:15:11,824
竜巻相手じゃ意味がない
but it's useless against the tornadoes.

235
00:15:11,824 --> 00:15:14,624
だから次は絶対勝つために
So next time, to make sure I win,

236
00:15:14,624 --> 00:15:18,024
僕はE缶だけは最後まで取っておく
I'll save my E-Tanks until the very end.

237
00:15:18,024 --> 00:15:23,024
倒せないよー
I can't defeat him!

238
00:16:31,024 --> 00:16:35,024
ロボのテーマ / 作曲：光田康典
Robo's Theme / Composition: Yasunori Mitsuda

239
00:16:37,524 --> 00:16:39,524
R・O・B・O
R-O-B-O

240
00:16:39,524 --> 00:16:42,524
ロボのテーマ
Robo's Theme

241
00:16:43,024 --> 00:16:46,524
鋼の体 夢を乗せて
Steel body, carrying dreams,

242
00:16:46,524 --> 00:16:50,024
未来を拓く 戦士なのさ
a warrior who opens the way to the future.

243
00:16:50,524 --> 00:16:54,024
壊れた心 直してくれた
You repaired my broken heart,

244
00:16:54,024 --> 00:16:57,524
優しい君の 笑顔守る
I'll protect your kind smile.

245
00:16:58,024 --> 00:17:01,524
遥か時空を 越えてゆこう
Let's go beyond far-off space-time,

246
00:17:01,524 --> 00:17:05,024
終わらない旅 続けよう
let's continue this never-ending journey.

247
00:17:05,524 --> 00:17:09,024
奇跡の歌を 響かせて
Let the song of miracles resonate,

248
00:17:09,024 --> 00:17:13,024
愛を届ける ロボのテーマ
delivering love, Robo's Theme.

249
00:17:13,024 --> 00:17:15,524
R・O・B・O
R-O-B-O

250
00:17:15,524 --> 00:17:18,024
ロボのテーマ
Robo's Theme

251
00:17:30,024 --> 00:17:34,024
カエルのテーマ / 作曲：光田康典
Frog's Theme / Composition: Yasunori Mitsuda

252
00:17:35,524 --> 00:17:39,024
勇気を胸に 剣を抜け
Draw your sword with courage in your heart,

253
00:17:39,024 --> 00:17:42,524
呪われた身の 騎士ならば
if you are a knight in a cursed body.

254
00:17:43,024 --> 00:17:46,524
誇り高き その魂
That high-proud soul,

255
00:17:46,524 --> 00:17:50,024
悪を貫く 閃光となれ
become the flash that pierces evil.

256
00:17:50,024 --> 00:17:52,524
カエル！
Frog!

257
00:17:52,524 --> 00:17:55,524
正義のヒーロー
Hero of justice.

258
00:17:56,024 --> 00:17:59,524
水面を跳ねて 闇を裂け
Leap across the water and tear through the darkness,

259
00:17:59,524 --> 00:18:03,024
勝利の旗を 掲げよう
let's raise the flag of victory.

260
00:18:03,524 --> 00:18:07,024
友との絆 忘れない
I won't forget the bond with my friend,

261
00:18:07,024 --> 00:18:10,524
誓いのメダル 輝かせて
make the Medal of Vow shine.

262
00:18:11,024 --> 00:18:14,524
時代の風を 追い越して
Overtake the winds of the era,

263
00:18:14,524 --> 00:18:18,024
明日へ駆ける カエルのテーマ
running toward tomorrow, Frog's Theme.

264
00:18:18,024 --> 00:18:20,524
カエル！
Frog!

265
00:18:20,524 --> 00:18:23,524
カエルのテーマ
Frog's Theme

266
00:19:22,024 --> 00:19:30,024
Melodies Of Life / 作詞：シオミ 作曲：植松伸夫
Melodies Of Life / Lyrics: Shiomi, Composition: Nobuo Uematsu

267
00:19:35,024 --> 00:19:42,024
あてもなく彷徨っていた
Wandering aimlessly,

268
00:19:42,024 --> 00:19:49,024
手がかりもなく探し続けた
searching without a clue.

269
00:19:49,024 --> 00:19:57,024
あなたがくれた思い出を
The memories you gave me,

270
00:19:57,024 --> 00:20:03,024
心を癒す歌にして
turning them into a song to heal my heart.

271
00:20:03,024 --> 00:20:08,024
約束の場所へ
To the promised place...

272
00:20:08,024 --> 00:20:11,024
いつか
someday.

273
00:20:00,032 --> 00:20:03,532
歌にして
...into a song to heal the heart.

274
00:20:07,532 --> 00:20:14,232
約束も無く 交わす言葉も
With no promise, and words we exchanged...

275
00:20:14,232 --> 00:20:21,032
決めることさえせず 抱きしめ
...without even deciding, we held each other tight.

276
00:20:21,032 --> 00:20:27,832
そして確かめた日々は
And the days we spent together...

277
00:20:27,832 --> 00:20:34,032
二度とは帰らぬ
...will never return.

278
00:20:36,832 --> 00:20:42,832
記憶の中の 手を振るあなたは
In my memories, you reaching out to me...

279
00:20:42,832 --> 00:20:49,232
私の名を呼ぶことができ
...can you still...

280
00:20:49,232 --> 00:20:54,032
きるの？
...call out my name?

281
00:21:03,532 --> 00:21:10,032
溢れるその涙を
Those overflowing tears...

282
00:21:10,032 --> 00:21:17,032
輝く夢に替えて
...change them into a shining dream.

283
00:21:17,032 --> 00:21:23,532
命は続く
Life goes on,

284
00:21:23,532 --> 00:21:27,532
夜を越え
crossing the night,

285
00:21:27,532 --> 00:21:37,032
疑うことのない明日へと続く
to a tomorrow without doubt...

286
00:21:37,032 --> 00:21:42,032
続く
...it continues.

287
00:22:22,032 --> 00:22:28,832
飛ぶ鳥の向こうの空へ
To the sky beyond the flying birds,

288
00:22:28,832 --> 00:22:36,232
幾つの記憶預けただろう
how many memories did I entrust?

289
00:22:36,232 --> 00:22:42,832
はかない希望も夢も
Fleeting hopes and dreams,

290
00:22:42,832 --> 00:22:51,032
届かぬ場所に忘れて
forgetting them in an unreachable place.

291
00:22:51,032 --> 00:22:59,032
めぐりあうのは
Our meeting,

292
00:22:59,032 --> 00:23:05,532
偶然と言えるの？
can we call it coincidence?

293
00:23:05,532 --> 00:23:12,532
分かってる
I know.

294
00:23:12,532 --> 00:23:19,532
時が必ずくれる
Time will surely give us...

295
00:23:19,532 --> 00:23:21,832
不意に
Suddenly,

296
00:23:21,832 --> 00:23:26,532
消えゆく運命でも
even if it's a destiny that fades away,

297
00:23:26,532 --> 00:23:33,232
君が生きている限り
as long as you are living,

298
00:23:33,232 --> 00:23:40,032
命は続く
life goes on,

299
00:23:40,032 --> 00:23:46,032
永遠に
forever.

300
00:23:46,032 --> 00:23:52,032
その力の限り どこまでも
With all its power, everywhere,

301
00:23:52,032 --> 00:23:58,532
私が死ぬとも
Even if I should pass away,

302
00:23:58,532 --> 00:24:09,032
君が生きている限り
as long as you are living,

303
00:24:09,032 --> 00:24:16,032
命は続く
life goes on,

304
00:24:16,032 --> 00:24:22,032
永遠に
forever.

305
00:24:22,032 --> 00:24:31,032
その力の限り どこまでも
With all its power, everywhere,

306
00:24:31,032 --> 00:24:36,532
続く
it continues.

307
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:15,540
きみの瞳に映る
Reflected in your eyes,

308
00:25:15,540 --> 00:25:21,840
わたしは何色ですか
what color am I?

309
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:29,040
赤深き望むなら
If you wish for a deep red,

310
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:35,840
渡そう陽の光を
I will give you the sunlight.

311
00:26:01,340 --> 00:26:06,840
悲しみが溢れ
Sadness overflowed...

312
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:13,040
瞼閉じました
and I closed my eyes.

313
00:26:13,540 --> 00:26:19,040
こぼれた滴は
The spilled drops...

314
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:25,040
心に沁みゆく
soak into my heart.

315
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:31,040
行き渡る波は
The spreading waves...

316
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:37,040
弱く交えます
mingle weakly.

317
00:26:37,540 --> 00:26:43,040
とどけしゆりかご
The cradle I sent...

318
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:49,040
眠りをさそう
invites sleep.

319
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:55,240
夢になつかし
In my dreams, I search...

320
00:26:55,240 --> 00:27:01,040
面影をさがす
for a familiar face.

321
00:27:01,040 --> 00:27:07,040
手を伸ばし 強く
I reach out my hand and...

322
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:14,040
抱きしめたくなる
I want to hold you tight.

323
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:22,840
きみの瞳に映る
Reflected in your eyes,

324
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:28,240
わたしは何色ですか
what color am I?

325
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:34,040
赤深き望むなら
If you wish for a deep red,

326
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:41,040
渡そう高き空を
I will give you the high sky.

327
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:57,240
不安定な神様
Unstable God,

328
00:27:57,240 --> 00:28:01,040
繰り返す出会いと別れ
Repeating meetings and partings.

329
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:04,240
また会えるその日まで
Until the day we can meet again,

330
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:08,540
時駆ける旅人
time-traveling traveler.

331
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:21,240
あなたが泣いている
You are crying.

332
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:24,240
流るる涙の雨
A rain of flowing tears.

333
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:27,840
慰めとは言わない
I won't call it comfort.

334
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:30,340
心悲しくて
With a sad heart,

335
00:28:30,340 --> 00:28:33,240
生きていけぬもの
those who cannot live on,

336
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:36,540
何かを背負いながら
while carrying something,

337
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:39,240
見えない鎖に
to invisible chains,

338
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:43,040
繋がれている
they are connected.

339
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:48,540
どれほど救われただろう
How much have I been saved?

340
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:52,040
あどけない笑顔を
That innocent smile,

341
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:55,540
なくしたくはない
I don't want to lose it.

342
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:59,240
不安定な神様
Unstable God,

343
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:02,840
繰り返すことなき運命
a fate that never repeats.

344
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:08,240
生まれて そして 死んでゆく定め
A destiny of being born and then dying.

345
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:11,240
かけちがえた世界で
In a world where we missed each other,

346
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:15,040
繰り返す出会いと別れ
repeating meetings and partings.

347
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:18,240
また会えるその日まで
Until the day we can meet again,

348
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:22,540
時駆ける旅人
time-traveling traveler.

349
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:25,540
戦闘開始！！
Combat Start!!

350
00:29:26,540 --> 00:29:28,040
鳥？
A bird?

351
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:31,040
デカっ！？
It's huge!?

352
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:35,840
禍々しき心
